'''天主教吉大港總教區'''（{{lang-la|Archidioecesis Chittagongensis}}）是[[孟加拉國|孟加拉國]]的一個[[羅馬天主教|羅馬天主教]]教省總教區，下轄兩個教區。總教區位於孟加拉國東南部，管轄[[吉大港專區|吉大港專區]]和[[達卡專區|達卡專區]]南部。

教區於1927年5月25日成立<ref>{{cite book |title=ACTA APOSTOLICAE SEDIS |volume=XIX |year=1927 |publisher=Typis Polyglottis Vaticanis |pages=374-375 |url=https://www.vatican.va/archive/aas/documents/AAS-19-1927-ocr.pdf |accessdate=2020-04-09 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200409173428/https://www.vatican.va/archive/aas/documents/AAS-19-1927-ocr.pdf |archivedate=2020-04-09 |language=la |dead-url=no }}</ref>，2017年2月2日升為總教區<ref>{{cite press release |title=Other Pontifical Acts, 02.02.2017 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2017/02/02/170202b.html |publisher=Holy See Press Office |accessdate=2020-07-26 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200726054701/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2017/02/02/170202b.html |archivedate=2020-07-26 |language=en |date=2017-02-02 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

教區於2007年時有32,743名教友（佔轄區總人口0.1%）、11個[[堂區|堂區]]、30名[[司鐸|司鐸]]、30名修士和87名修女。主教座堂為{{link-en|玫瑰聖母主教座堂 (吉大港)|Our Lady of the Holy Rosary Cathedral, Chittagong|玫瑰聖母主教座堂}}。總主教現時[[教座出缺|出缺]]<ref>{{cite news |last1=Mares |first1=Courtney |title=At least 9 Catholic bishops have died from the coronavirus |url=https://www.catholicnewsagency.com/news/at-least-9-catholic-bishops-have-died-from-the-coronavirus-94157 |accessdate=2020-07-24 |publisher=Catholic News Agency |date=2020-07-20 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200724125135/https://www.catholicnewsagency.com/news/at-least-9-catholic-bishops-have-died-from-the-coronavirus-94157 |archivedate=2020-07-24 |language=en |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

